@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #0F172A
  LifeLineBorderColor #334155
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  ParticipantBorderColor #334155
}

title Sequence - Hủy đặt vé

actor User as "Khách hàng"
participant UI as "[[../../client/src/features/user/components/BookingDetailModal.tsx BookingDetail/HistoryPage]]"
participant Hook as "[[../../client/src/features/booking/hooks/useBookingGuard.ts cancelBookingApi flow]]"
participant API as "[[../../client/src/lib/api-client.ts apiClient]]"
control Ctl as "[[../../src/main/java/com/mecinema/mecinema/controller/booking/BookingController.java BookingController]]"
participant Svc as "[[../../src/main/java/com/mecinema/mecinema/service/BookingService.java BookingService]]"
database Repo as "[[../../src/main/java/com/mecinema/mecinema/repo/BookingRepository.java BookingRepository]]"

User -> UI: Bấm hủy đơn đặt vé
UI -> UI: Hiển thị hộp thoại xác nhận
User -> UI: Xác nhận hủy
UI -> Hook: [[../../client/src/features/booking/hooks/useBookingGuard.ts cancelBookingApi(bookingId)]]
Hook -> API: [[../../client/src/features/booking/services/booking.service.ts cancelBookingApi(id)]] DELETE /api/bookings/{bookingId}
API -> Ctl: [[../../src/main/java/com/mecinema/mecinema/controller/booking/BookingController.java#L59 cancelBooking(currentUser, bookingId)]]
Ctl -> Svc: [[../../src/main/java/com/mecinema/mecinema/service/BookingService.java cancelBooking(userId, bookingId)]]
Svc -> Repo: [[../../src/main/java/com/mecinema/mecinema/repo/BookingRepository.java findByIdAndUserId(bookingId, userId)]]
alt Không hợp lệ hoặc không tồn tại
  Svc --> Ctl: throw exception
  Ctl --> API: 400/404
  API --> UI: Thông báo hủy thất bại
else Hợp lệ
  Svc -> Svc: booking.setStatus(FAILED)
  Svc -> Svc: Giải phóng ghế đã giữ
  Svc --> Ctl: done
  Ctl --> API: 204 No Content
  API --> UI: Cập nhật trạng thái đơn
  UI --> User: Thông báo hủy thành công
end
@enduml

